Source: licq
Build-Depends: cdbs (>= 0.4.52), debhelper (>= 6.0.7), imagemagick, kdebase-data (>= 4:3.97.0), kdelibs4-dev, libcdk5-dev, libgpgme11-dev (>= 0.4.2), libncurses5-dev, libqt3-mt-dev, libssl-dev, libxosd-dev (>= 2.1.0), libxss-dev, libboost-dev (>= 1.13.1)
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Erik Johansson <debian@ejohansson.se>
Standards-Version: 3.8.0
